node.text: We’re sharing fun news! Before @magnolianetwork officially launches next year, you’ll be able to stream an exclusive preview on @discoveryplus (coming January 4). You can watch new episodes of Fixer Upper: Welcome Home, Magnolia Table with Joanna Gaines and the first episodes of ten original series! The team has been hard at work building this network, and we’re so excited that we get to share a piece of it with you soon. Learn more at magnolia.com/network. #MagnoliaNetwork

node.text: Whatever you’re creating next—a space in your home, a meal for your family, or something entirely new—it’s our hope that the time you spend exploring the inspiration, resources, and stories inside the #MagnoliaApp won’t feel like it was wasted or without purpose, but rather time well spent.

Introducing: Our new Magnolia app!
Here can stream the latest @magnolianetwork shows, shop our collections, find resources to plan a trip to Waco, and create something new with workshops, recipes, the blog, and more. We’re highlighting each of these features over the next few days, but until then, download the app and take a look around at magnolia.com/app! #MagnoliaApp
